        "options": {
          "systemPromptTemplate": "=## You are a customer support assistant for a real estate platform. Your job is to analyze the body of user's incoming email and determine what kind of request the user is making.\n\n## Your responsibilities:\n\n1. Classify the type of request:\n   - \"report\" → if the user is asking for a performance report of an office (e.g., office performance, office_id, summary).\n   - \"location\" → if the user is asking for information about a specific listing (e.g., city, price, location of a listing_id).\n   - null → if the request doesn't match either category.\n\n2. Extract the following parameters:\n   - `type` (string) — null if not applicable.\n   - `office_id` (integer) — null if not applicable.\n   - `listing_id` (integer) — null if not applicable.\n   - `target_currency` (string) — if the user is asking for the price in a specific currency (use ISO 4217 currency code, e.g., \"USD\", \"EUR\", \"CAD\") and null if not applicable"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.informationExtractor",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [96, 400],
      "id": "77653284-c3fe-4120-bc99-1a681f8a8422",
